{"tid":1913737,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"返工期間用公司車撞到對方車輛","createTime":"2020-03-07T04:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T16:29:36.000Z","uid":125759,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"70e2714c14452cd0b0983c51ee40d1c3a9c381c6","tid":1913737,"uid":125759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:49:23.000Z","msg":"上年年頭反工期間用公司車撞到對方架車，上年年尾左右上左庭承認左不小心架駛。而架車當時係公司租反黎用住先。<br />\n今日收到對方律師樓既一疊信，但信入面冇寫賠償金額，反而有對方睇醫生既紙生紙。<br />\n我即時搵反舊公司相討，我問舊公司有冇報保險，佢好婉轉答冇，公司話保險唔係落我名所以claim唔到。<br />\n咁我想問下我下一步應該要點做？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔左咁耐保險公司都應該唔受保<br />\n另外想問一下關唔關勞工法例事？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160c21c581b221b193826a51b7484d470e5e5e4f","tid":1913737,"uid":62192,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:00:06.000Z","msg":"你等破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f08062dd6221bc10835c16fd8f47040934b0abe","tid":1913737,"uid":39069,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"第一你認左老不 (無報保險既情況下).<br />\n第二你揸車撞到人地架車係你既責任<br />\n第三你收到律師信即係對方循民事追究你<br />\n<br />\n拖左成年我諗你岩岩撞果陣人地搵你你無理到?<br />\n而家判左你老不 你上到法庭都輸左9成9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你預左要賠錢 仲要預返金額唔細<br />\n去到呢步我諗都好難和解...搵律師幫你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d4f8b8d53467eee6619a8a6f6de4ed5c06c0dc","tid":1913737,"uid":62935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"嘩 lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1bbf60b88173f078ad150be4c3e4ae493a2fe8","tid":1913737,"uid